<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٢٠٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6401">مُوسَى بْنُ</a><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">إِسْمَاعِيلَ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6858">وُهَيْبٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3667">أَبِي قِلَابَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَتْ أُمُّ سُلَيْمٍ فِي الثَّقَلِ وَأَنْجَشَةُ غُلَامُ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يَسُوقُ بِهِنَّ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> يَا أَنْجَشَُ رُوَيْدَكَ سَوْقَكَ بِالْقَوَارِيرِ.»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>